<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Shipping Policy</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/Policy.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
    <main>
        <header>
            <h1>Shipping Policy</h1>
        </header>
        <section>
            <h2>Shipping Methods and Delivery Times</h2>
            <p>We offer standard and express shipping options.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Standard shipping typically takes 5-7 business days.</li>
                <li>Express shipping typically takes 2-3 business days.</li>
                <li>Orders placed before 12 PM (local time) will be processed and shipped the same day.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Shipping Rates</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Standard shipping is free for orders over ₹500.</li>
                <li>For orders under ₹500, standard shipping costs ₹50.</li>
                <li>Express shipping costs ₹150 regardless of the order amount.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>International Shipping</h2>
            <p>We currently do not offer international shipping.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Shipping Confirmation and Order Tracking</h2>
            <p>Once your order has shipped, you will receive a shipping confirmation email with tracking information.</p>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
